- **`process.rs`** -- `ChromiumProcess` declared as an empty unit struct.

None of the modules contain any implementations or logic. The crate defines the structural skeleton (module layout, public types, dependency wiring) but no actual functionality has been written yet. Everything is commented as a placeholder for "Phase 1 (Browser Control)".
